<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Professional Resume Template</title>
    <!-- Importing a stylish, highly legible font pairing -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <style>
        /* CSS VARIABLES 
           Updated with the new "Inter" font stack.
        */
        :root {
            --primary-text: #111827;
            --secondary-text: #4b5563;
            --accent-color: #1d4ed8;
            --border-color: #e5e7eb;
            --font-main: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
            --page-width: 210mm; /* A4 Width */
            --page-height: 297mm; /* A4 Height */
        }

        /* RESET & BASE STYLES */
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: var(--font-main);
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: var(--primary-text);
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
            -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
            -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
        }

        /* PAGE CONTAINER */
        .resume-page {
            background: white;
            width: var(--page-width);
            min-height: var(--page-height);
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 50px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        /* PRINT STYLING */
        @media print {
            body {
                background: none;
            }
            .resume-page {
                margin: 0;
                box-shadow: none;
                width: 100%;
                height: 100%;
                padding: 0.5in;
            }
            @page {
                size: A4;
                margin: 0;
            }
            section, .experience-item, .education-item {
                page-break-inside: avoid;
            }
        }

        /* HEADER & CONTACT INFO */
        header {
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 3px solid var(--accent-color);
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 28pt;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -0.025em;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            color: #000;
        }

        .contact-info {
            font-size: 9.5pt;
            color: var(--secondary-text);
            font-weight: 400;
        }

        .contact-info span:not(:last-child)::after {
            content: " • ";
            margin: 0 8px;
            color: #9ca3af;
        }

        /* SECTION TITLES */
        h2 {
            font-size: 13pt;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            margin-top: 25px;
            color: var(--accent-color);
        }

        section {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        /* SUMMARY */
        .summary p {
            font-size: 10.5pt;
            color: var(--secondary-text);
        }

        /* EXPERIENCE & EDUCATION */
        .item-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: baseline;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 11pt;
            color: #000;
        }

        .item-subheader {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: var(--secondary-text);
            font-size: 10pt;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }

        ul {
            margin-left: 18px;
            font-size: 10pt;
            color: var(--secondary-text);
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        li {
            margin-bottom: 4px;
            padding-left: 5px;
        }

        /* SKILLS GRID */
        .skills-container {
            font-size: 10pt;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .skill-category {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--primary-text);
        }

        /* ACTIONS */
        .no-print {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding-bottom: 40px;
        }
        
        button {
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background-color: var(--accent-color);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-family: var(--font-main);
            transition: opacity 0.2s;
        }

        button:hover {
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        @media print {
            .no-print { display: none; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="resume-page">
        <!-- HEADER -->
        <header>
            <h1>John Doe</h1>
            <div class="contact-info">
                <span>San Francisco, CA</span>
                <span>(555) 000-0000</span>
                <span>john.doe@email.com</span>
                <span>linkedin.com/in/johndoe</span>
            </div>
        </header>

        <!-- PROFESSIONAL SUMMARY -->
        <section class="summary">
            <h2>Professional Summary</h2>
            <p>
                Highly motivated and results-oriented Professional with over 5 years of experience in high-growth technology sectors. Proven track record of optimizing complex workflows, leading diverse cross-functional teams, and delivering high-impact projects. Expert in bridging the gap between technical requirements and business objectives.
            </p>
        </section>

        <!-- EXPERIENCE -->
        <section class="experience">
            <h2>Work Experience</h2>
            
            <div class="experience-item">
                <div class="item-header">
                    <span>Senior Project Manager</span>
                    <span>Jan 2020 – Present</span>
                </div>
                <div class="item-subheader">
                    <span>Tech Solutions Inc.</span>
                    <span>San Francisco, CA</span>
                </div>
                <ul>
                    <li>Led a team of 15 developers to launch a mobile application that gained 100k+ downloads in the first quarter.</li>
                    <li>Reduced operational costs by 15% through the implementation of automated CI/CD pipelines.</li>
                    <li>Collaborated with stakeholders to define project scope and technical requirements for multi-million dollar contracts.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="experience-item">
                <div class="item-header">
                    <span>Junior Operations Analyst</span>
                    <span>June 2017 – Dec 2019</span>
                </div>
                <div class="item-subheader">
                    <span>DataCorp Systems</span>
                    <span>Austin, TX</span>
                </div>
                <ul>
                    <li>Analyzed large datasets using SQL and Python to identify market trends, resulting in a 10% increase in sales leads.</li>
                    <li>Streamlined internal reporting processes, saving the department approximately 20 man-hours per week.</li>
                    <li>Assisted in the migration of legacy data to cloud-based infrastructure (AWS).</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- EDUCATION -->
        <section class="education">
            <h2>Education</h2>
            <div class="education-item">
                <div class="item-header">
                    <span>Bachelor of Science in Computer Science</span>
                    <span>Graduated May 2017</span>
                </div>
                <div class="item-subheader">
                    <span>University of State</span>
                    <span>GPA: 3.8/4.0</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- SKILLS -->
        <section class="skills">
            <h2>Skills</h2>
            <div class="skills-container">
                <p><span class="skill-category">Technical:</span> Python, SQL, JavaScript, React, AWS, Docker, Git, CI/CD.</p>
                <p><span class="skill-category">Soft Skills:</span> Project Management, Strategic Planning, Public Speaking, Agile/Scrum.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- CERTIFICATIONS -->
        <section class="certifications">
            <h2>Certifications</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Project Management Professional (PMP)</li>
                <li>AWS Certified Solutions Architect</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
    </div>

</body>
</html>